datasets.name: aab53035
queryLines:
WITH latest_jobs AS (
  SELECT
    workspace_id,
    job_id,
    name,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY workspace_id, job_id ORDER BY change_time DESC) as rn
  FROM system.lakeflow.jobs
  QUALIFY rn = 1
),
job_run_timeline_with_name AS (
  SELECT
    t.*,
    j.name as job_name
  FROM system.lakeflow.job_run_timeline t
  LEFT JOIN latest_jobs j
    ON t.workspace_id = j.workspace_id
    AND t.job_id = j.job_id
),
jobs_usage AS (
  SELECT
    *,
    usage_metadata.job_id,
    usage_metadata.job_run_id as run_id,
    identity_metadata.run_as as run_as
  FROM system.billing.usage
  WHERE billing_origin_product IN ("JOBS")
),
jobs_usage_with_usd AS (
  SELECT
    jobs_usage.*,
    --  * list_prices.pricing.effective_list.default
    usage_quantity * pricing.effective_list.default as usage_usd
  FROM jobs_usage
  LEFT JOIN system.billing.list_prices pricing ON
    jobs_usage.sku_name = pricing.sku_name
    AND pricing.price_start_time <= jobs_usage.usage_start_time
    AND (pricing.price_end_time >= jobs_usage.usage_start_time OR pricing.price_end_time IS NULL)
    AND pricing.currency_code = "USD"
),
jobs_usage_aggregated AS (
  SELECT
    workspace_id,
    job_id,
    run_id,
    usage_date, 
    FIRST(run_as, TRUE) as run_as,
    sku_name,
    SUM(usage_usd) as usage_usd,
    SUM(usage_quantity) as usage_quantity
  FROM jobs_usage_with_usd
  GROUP BY ALL
)
SELECT
  t1.*,
  MIN(t2.period_start_time) as run_start_time,
  MAX(t2.period_end_time) as run_end_time,
  TIMESTAMPDIFF(
      MINUTE,
      t2.period_start_time,
      t2.period_end_time
    ) AS duration_minutes,
    TIMESTAMPDIFF(
      HOUR,
      t2.period_start_time,
      t2.period_end_time 
    ) AS duration_hours,
  FIRST(t2.result_state, TRUE) as result_state,
  FIRST(t2.job_name, TRUE) as job_name
FROM jobs_usage_aggregated t1
LEFT JOIN job_run_timeline_with_name t2
  ON t1.workspace_id = t2.workspace_id
  AND t1.job_id = t2.job_id
  AND t1.run_id = t2.run_id
-- WHERE t2.job_name = 'submit_process_basic_listings'
-- where t1.workspace_id in (:workspace_id)
GROUP BY ALL
ORDER BY usage_usd DESC
-- LIMIT 100

datasets.name: e67e1af0
queryLines:
SELECT
  usage.account_id,
  usage.workspace_id,
  usage.sku_name,
  usage.cloud,
  usage.usage_start_time,
  usage.usage_end_time,
  usage.usage_date, 
  usage.usage_type,
  identity_metadata.run_as ,
  identity_metadata.created_by,
  COALESCE(identity_metadata.run_as, identity_metadata.owned_by) AS id,
  custom_tags,
  -- usage_metadata.*
  billing_origin_product,
  SUM(
    usage.usage_quantity * list_prices.pricing.effective_list.default
  ) AS `Total Dollar Cost`
FROM v_system.billing.usage
JOIN v_system.billing.list_prices
  ON list_prices.sku_name = usage.sku_name
  AND list_prices.price_start_time <= usage.usage_start_time
  AND (list_prices.price_end_time >= usage.usage_start_time OR list_prices.price_end_time IS NULL)
  AND list_prices.currency_code = "USD"
-- where usage.workspace_id in (:workspace_id)

GROUP BY ALL

datasets.name: 0754369c
queryLines:
SELECT
  usage.usage_metadata.job_id,
  usage.usage_metadata.job_name,
  SUM(usage.usage_quantity) AS total_dbu,
  SUM(
    usage.usage_quantity * pricing.default
  ) AS total_usd
FROM
  v_system.billing.usage AS usage
LEFT JOIN v_system.billing.list_prices AS pricing
  ON usage.sku_name = pricing.sku_name
  AND pricing.price_start_time <= usage.usage_start_time
  AND (
    pricing.price_end_time >= usage.usage_start_time
    OR pricing.price_end_time IS NULL
  )
  AND pricing.currency_code = 'USD'
WHERE
  usage.usage_metadata.job_id IS NOT NULL
  AND usage.usage_unit = 'DBU'
  AND usage.usage_date >= date_add(
    current_date,
    -CAST(:param_days AS INT)
  )
GROUP BY
  usage.usage_metadata.job_id,
  usage.usage_metadata.job_name
ORDER BY
  total_dbu DESC

datasets.name: 15b91a1d
queryLines:
SELECT
  usage_metadata.notebook_id,
  usage_metadata.notebook_path,
  SUM(usage_quantity) as total_dbu,
  SUM(
    usage.usage_quantity * pricing.default
  ) AS total_usd
FROM
  v_system.billing.usage AS usage
LEFT JOIN v_system.billing.list_prices AS pricing
  ON usage.sku_name = pricing.sku_name
  AND pricing.price_start_time <= usage.usage_start_time
  AND (
    pricing.price_end_time >= usage.usage_start_time
    OR pricing.price_end_time IS NULL
  )
  AND pricing.currency_code = 'USD'
WHERE
  usage_metadata.notebook_id is not null
  and billing_origin_product = 'INTERACTIVE'
  and product_features.is_serverless
  and  usage.usage_unit = 'DBU'
  and  usage.usage_date >= DATEADD(day,-CAST(:param_days AS INT), current_date)
GROUP BY
  ALL
ORDER BY
  total_dbu DESC

datasets.name: a5e6c46a
queryLines:
SELECT
  COALESCE(identity_metadata.run_as, identity_metadata.owned_by) AS id,
  usage_metadata.job_id,
  usage_metadata.job_name,
  usage_metadata.notebook_id,
  usage_metadata. notebook_path,
  SUM(usage_quantity) as total_dbu
FROM
  v_system.billing.usage
WHERE
--   identity_metadata.run_as = format_string('%s@%s.%s', :user_name, :domain_name, :top_level_domain)
--   and 
  usage_date >= DATEADD(day, -CAST(:param_days AS INT), current_date)
GROUP BY
  ALL
ORDER BY
  total_dbu DESC
